                    <item xml:id="e1">
                        <desc>The name of the original owner, <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13723DamaKr">Dama Krǝstos</persName> has been erased in the first third of the manuscript.
                            In a few of the erased spaces, the name of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13724BatraM">Batra Māryām</persName> had been originally written (e.g. <locus target="#24va #32rb"/>).
                            The name of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13653Ermeyas">ʾErmǝyās</persName> is mentioned on <locus target="#69r"/>.
                           The names of  <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS12814Mikael">ሚካኤል፡</persName> and 
                            <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS12815Fasikawit">ፋሲካይት፡</persName> have been written over the erasures.
                            Rarely, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ንጉሥነ፡ ኢያሱ፡</foreign>, 
                            probably to be identified with <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5616IyasuI">ʾIyāsu I</persName> or <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5617IyasuII">ʾIyāsu II</persName>, has also been written above the 
                        erasure (e.g. <locus target="#4rb"/>).</desc>
                    </item>
                                    
                              
